{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"16280","heading":"Advanced Nuclear Energy Licensing Cost-Share Grant Program","label":"16280 Advanced Nuclear Energy Licensing Cost-Share Grant Program","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch149/schIX/ptE","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Nuclear Energy Innovation Capabilities Act of 2017, and not as part of the Energy Policy Act of 2005 which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Commission","label":"1 Commission","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “Commission” means the Nuclear Regulatory Commission.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Program","label":"2 Program","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “program” means the Advanced Nuclear Energy Cost-Share Grant Program established under subsection (b).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Secretary","label":"3 Secretary","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of Energy.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Establishment","label":"b Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall establish a grant program, to be known as the “Advanced Nuclear Energy Cost-Share Grant Program”, under which the Secretary shall make cost-share grants to applicants for the purpose of funding a portion of the Commission fees of the applicant for pre-application review activities and application review activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Requirement","label":"c Requirement","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall seek out technology diversity in making grants under the program.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Cost-share amount","label":"d Cost-share amount","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall determine the cost-share amount for each grant under the program in accordance with .section 16352 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Use of funds","label":"e Use of funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"developing a licensing project plan;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"obtaining a statement of licensing feasibility;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fe%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"reviewing topical reports; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16280/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16280%2Fe%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","headi